Demo Setup
----------------------

- Download and install Android SDK

https://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html
Or, easiest way is to install Android Studio.


- Download go1.5 and build for your host.

- Set the environment variables listed in the demo.rc for your environment.
If you use bash, modify the demo.rc and run `source demo.rc`

- Install the gomobile tool and run init before demo.

% go install golang.org/x/mobile/cmd/gomobile
% gomobile init

- Hello Gopher demo

% demo1.bash

- Gobind demo

% demo2.bash

Enjoy.
